  Different hypotheses about the \PW+jets background distribution are considered: nonrestricted background model parameters, 
  or parameters fixed to the central values as summarized in Table~\ref{tab:wlanparams}. 
  The quoted uncertainty in the cross section is the total uncertainty~\citeAN{AN-17-043}.\label{tab:signif}} 
\begin{center}
 \begin{tabular}{c|cc|cc}
 \toprule
  Hypothesis & \multicolumn{2}{c|}{All event categories} & \multicolumn{2}{c}{1$\ell$4j2\cPqb} \\
  & \stt [nb] & Significance & \stt [nb] & Significance \\
  \midrule
  Nominal & $45\pm8$ & 6.64 & $49\pm13$ & 5.95 \\
  \midrule
