The PLR variation as a function of the parameter of interest, and corresponding to the different hypotheses about the \PW+jets model parameters, 
are given in Figs.~\ref{fig:lhscan_nominal}-~\ref{fig:lhscan_model2} for all three event categories. 
The breakdown into statistical and systematic uncertainties is slightly different from the procedure followed to quote the result in Eq.\,(\ref{eq:xsection_pPb_perchannel}); 
the background normalization is included in the statistical uncertainty, while they are treated as a source of systematic uncertainty in Eq.\,(\ref{eq:xsection_pPb_perchannel})x.

